2023 College Football Schedule

Share Tweet Email

The 2023 college football schedule kicks off in Week Zero on Saturday, August 26.

Below is the college football schedule by week for the Football Bowl Subdivision (FBS). Rankings are based on ESPN’s Way Too Early Top 25 until the release of the AP Top 25 Poll this summer.

We also have a weekly FCS Schedule and a College Football TV Schedule that includes all FBS and FCS games.

By purchasing tickets using the affiliate links below, you'll help support FBSchedules. We may receive a small commission.
